claim.claim-text:
1. A method of facilitating conversation between at least two dining partners, said method comprising: 
a) providing a set of open-ended questions each being separately printed on a surface of a dining-piece; 
b) distributing one or more of the dining-pieces to each dining partner; 
c) having each dining partner read aloud the open-ended question printed on their dining-piece; 
d) having one of the dining partners answer aloud said open-ended question; and 
e) engaging at least one other of the dining partners in open discussion of alternate answers to said question.

9. A method of promoting discussion between dining partners, said method comprising: 
a) providing tableware having an open-ended question printed on a surface thereof; 
b) distributing said tableware to at least one of the dining partners; 
c) having each dining partner read aloud said open-ended question printed on their respective tableware; 
d) having one of the dining partners answer aloud said open-ended question; and 
e) engaging all of the dining partners in open discussion regarding said open-ended question.

11. A method of facilitating conversation between at least two dining partners, said method comprising: 
a) providing tableware having a command printed on a surface thereof; 
b) distributing said tableware to at least one of the dining partners; 
c) having each dining partner read aloud the command printed on their dining-piece; 
d) having one of the dining, partners answer aloud the command; and 
e) engaging at least one other of the dining partners in open discussion of alternate responses to the command.
